<p>åˆ©ç”¨ Householder å˜æ¢æ±‚ $\boldsymbol{A}$ çš„ $\mathrm{QR}$ åˆ†è§£ã€‚</p>

<p>è§£ï¼š$\boldsymbol{s}<em>1 = [0,1,0]^{\top}$,  $e_1 = [1, 0, 0]^{\top}$,  $c_1 = -\mathrm{sgn}(a</em> {11})\Vert s_1 \Vert = 1$, $u_1 = s_1-c_1e_1 = [-1,1,0]^{\top}$,</p>

