<p>$\boldsymbol{s}<em>2 = [0,4,3]^{\top}$($H_2A_1$ ä¸æ”¹å˜ $A_1$ çš„ç¬¬ä¸€è¡Œ)ï¼Œ$e_2 = [0, 1, 0]^{\top}$,  $c_2 = -\mathrm{sgn}(a</em> {22})\Vert s_2 \Vert = -5$,  $u_2 = s_2-c_2e_2 = [0,9,3]^{\top}$,</p>

